data.description: This newly updated home has an open concept and comes complete with 2 living rooms, a welcoming kitchen/dining area, study, 5 bedrooms, and 2.1 bathrooms. Fresh Paint, Updated and very stylish bathrooms, kitchen, and laundry room. It features shiplap walls, built in shelving, and a sliding bard door. There is a workshop in the backyard with concrete floors, and electricity.
